Package: futureverse
Title: Easily Install and Load the 'Futureverse'
Version: 0.0.0-9003
Imports:
    future,
    future.apply,
    furrr,
    doFuture,
    progressr
Suggests:
    future.batchtools,
    future.callr,
    future.mirai
Authors@R: c(person("Henrik", "Bengtsson", role=c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
                                          email = "henrikb@braju.com"))
Description: The 'futureverse' is a set of packages for parallel and distributed process with the 'future' package at its core. This package is designed to make it easy to install and load multiple 'futureverse' packages in a single step. Learn more about the 'futureverse' at <https://www.futureverse.org>. This package is intended for end-users and R scripts. Packages must not list it as a dependency - instead, declare each Futureverse package needed.
